         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">4/3/95 ¶  ¶ Let me thank you, dear Madam, for your thoughtfulness in sending the reviving lichen. I found it on the Murray-River in my travels of 1848 already. Such specimens are always very acceptabl...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">95.03.04a</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To Ellen Burkitt</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">Private hands.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">4/3/95</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Let me thank you, dear Madam, for your thoughtfulness in sending the reviving lichen. I found it on the Murray-River in my travels of 1848 already. Such specimens are always very acceptable for foreign interchanges. Could you induce children or Amateurs to collect for me any floating or submerged weeds there? The aquatic plants of your region have never yet been fully investigated. Can I send you anything very acceptable from here?</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">With regardful remembrance</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>your</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Best compliments to my old friend, Mr Burkitt<note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">William Christopher Burkitt; see E. Burkitt to M, 16 July 1884.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Does the Reverend Pastor Kempe live near you?</p>
         </div>
      </body>
